text: The Islamic Azad University, Meymeh Branchhttp://www.iaumeymeh.ac.ir is a university in the town of Meymeh in Isfahan Province, Iran. It is a branch of the Islamic Azad University, one of the largest universities in the world. ==References== Meymeh, Islamic Azad University of Category:Buildings and structures in Isfahan Province Category:Education in Isfahan Province
